87-zayavlenie-a-zakaeva-v-svyazi-s-teraktom-v-bostone.html |archivedate=April 22, 2013 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AutoLC-157\">{{cite news|first1=Courtney|last1=Weaver|first2=Charles|last2=Clover|url=http://www.ft.com/intl/cms/s/0/8c2ddf8e-aa80-11e2-bc0d-00144feabdc0.html|title=Russian militant group denies Boston link|newspaper=The [[Financial Times]] | date=April 21, 2013 |accessdate= April 11, 2015|quote=The main militant group in Russia's southern Caucasus region, the Caucasus Emirate, has denied responsibility for last week's Boston bombing}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AutoLC-158\">{{cite web|url=http://www.rferl.org/content/daghestan-insurgency-denies-any-role-in-boston-bombing/24964774.html|title=Daghestani Insurgency Denies Any Role in Boston Bombings |publisher=Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty|date=April 13, 2013|accessdate=April 22, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AutoLC-159\">{{cite web|url=http://www.kavkaz.org.uk/eng/content/2013/04/21/17679.shtml |title=Statement of the Command of Mujahideen of Caucasus Emirate's Dagestan Province in relation to events in Boston |publisher=Kavkaz.org.uk |accessdate=April 22, 2013 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140207095208/http://www.kavkaz.org.uk/eng/content/2013/04/21/17679.shtml |archivedate=February 7, 2014 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AutoLC-160\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/one-day-after-boston-bombing-new-york-post-has-not-retracted-presumably-incorrect-reports-death-toll#|title=One Day After Boston Bombing, New York Post Has Not Retracted Presumably Incorrect Reports of Death Toll and Saudi Suspect |work=International Business Times|accessdate=April 22, 2013|last=Killoran |first=Ellen |date=April 16, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AutoLC-163\">{{cite web|url=http://www.mediabistro.com/fishbowlny/ny-post-fail-police-journalists-refute-tabloids-report-of-arrested-suspect_b80589 |title=NY Post Fail? Police Deny Tabloid's Report of Suspect 'Under Guard{{'-|accessdate= April 11, 2015