aku.com/the-sonic-the-hedgehog-movie-was-originally-scheduled-t-1842146174 | work = [[Kotaku]] | location = | access-date = March 16, 2020 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200321010612/https://kotaku.com/the-sonic-the-hedgehog-movie-was-originally-scheduled-t-1842146174 | archive-date = March 21, 2020 | url-status = live}}</ref> until further notice\n|-\n|''[[Sooryavanshi]]'' || {{dts|March 24, 2020}} || TBA<ref name=\"ABPLive\" />\n|-\n|''[[Soul (2020 film)|Soul]]'' || {{dts|June 19, 2020}} || {{dts|November 20, 2020}}<ref name=\"SoulNovember\" />\n|-\n|''[[Spiral (2020 film)|Spiral]]'' || {{dts|May 15, 2020}} || TBA<ref name=\"Spiral\" />\n|-\n|''[[The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge on the Run]]'' || {{dts|May 22, 2020}} || {{dts|August 7, 2020}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/04/the-spongebob-movie-sponge-on-the-run-new-release-date-1202908177/|title=''The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge On the Run'' Takes Over ''Infinite''s Early August Slot|work=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|date=April 14, 2020|access-date=April 14, 2020}}</ref> (Replacing ''[[Infinite (film)|Infinite]]'', released on later date) \n|-\n|''[[Stand by Me Doraemon 2]]'' || {{dts|August 7, 2020}} || TBA<ref name=\"Doremon2\" />\n|-\n|''[[Thor: Love and Thunder]]'' || {{dts|November 5, 2021}} || {{dts|February 18, 2022}}<ref name=\"HollywoodNewDisney\" />{{efn|As part of the future MCU, the initial delay of ''Black Widow'' forced ''Love and Thunder'' to be pushed back, too.}}\n|-\n|''[[The Tomorrow War]]'' || {{dts|December 25, 2020}} || July 23, 2021<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/box-office/mission-impossible-sequels-get-pushed-back-1234589362/|title=\u2018Mission: Impossible\u2019 Sequels Get Pushed Back|last=Rubin|first=Rebecca|last2=Rubin|first2=Rebecca|date=2020-04-24|website=Variety|language=en|access-date=2020-04-24}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Top Gun: Maverick]]'' || {{dts|June 26, 2020}} || {{dts|December 23, 2020}}<ref name=\"ParamountChanges\" />\