a-Mihajlovics-grave\n |accessdate  = 30 July 2010\n |ref         = harv\n |url-status     = dead\n |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20110810033954/http://english.blic.rs/In-Focus/6091/Excavation-of-Draza-Mihajlovics-grave\n |archivedate = 10 August 2011\n |df          = dmy-all\n}}\n* {{cite book\n  | last = Freeman\n  | first = Gregory A.\n  | year = 2007\n  | title = The Forgotten 500: The Untold Story of the Men Who Risked All for the Greatest Rescue Mission of World War II\n  | publisher = New American Library\n  | location = [[New York City|New York]]\n  | isbn = 978-0-451-22495-8\n  | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=zkZJ6yHG-xwC\n  | ref = harv\n  }}\n* {{cite news\n  | newspaper = Glas javnosti\n  | date = 1 August 1999\n  | title = Gi\u0161ka and guards died for nothing\n  | url = http://arhiva.glas-javnosti.rs/arhiva/1999/08/02/srpski/R99080102.shtm\n  | ref = {{sfnRef|Glas javnosti|1999}}\n  }}\n* {{cite book |last1=Schramm |first1=Percy Ernst |last2=Greiner |first2=Helmuth |last3=Hubatsch |first3=Walther |date=1963 |title=Kriegstagebuch des Oberkommandos der Wehrmacht, Band III (1943), Zweiter Halbband |volume=III/2 |publisher=Bernard & Graefe Verlag f\u00fcr Wehrwesen |location=Frankfurt am Main |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite web\n  | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/worldwars/wwtwo/partisan_fighters_04.shtml\n  | title = Partisans: War in the Balkans 1941\u20131945\n  | first = Stephen A\n  | last = Hart\n  | date = 5 November 2009\n  | publisher = BBC\n  | accessdate = 23 May 2010\n  | ref = harv\n  }}\n* {{cite journal\n  | last = Hehn\n  | first = Paul N.\n  | authorlink = \n  | year = 1971\n  | title = Serbia, Croatia and Germany 1941\u20131945: Civil War and Revolution in the Balkans\n  | journal = Canadian Slavonic Papers\n  | volume = 13\n  | issue = 4\n  | pages = 344\u2013373\n  | accessdate = 8 April 2012\n  | url = https://scholar.google.com.au/scholar?hl=en&q=Gebeit+des+serbien+hehn&btnG=Search&lr=lang_en&as_sdt=0%2C5&as_ylo=&as_v